Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配備著以電腦為導航系統的賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CYBER F0RMULA」正式登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替「F-l」的2l世紀賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令全世界人都狂熱起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,新世紀GPX 「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:33.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:40.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:43.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自你求助的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:53.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨夜開始一直感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:01:00.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其來的風暴阻擋了前進的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:04.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望便浮現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:08.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡 是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:15.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會放在心上 不論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的波浪會緊隨而來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:27.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上出發 決不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:33.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現夢想 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:36.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:43.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:50.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世界盃錦標賽的第一戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:01:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初嘗敗續的隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的沮喪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 當他親眼看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去曾經風光一時的賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在退出賽車生涯以後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然一心一意的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為生活而奮鬥的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深深受到感動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道自己的做法是幼稚的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就決定重新出發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 超級駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 他就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高速公路上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟隼人一直救出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被綁架小女孩的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教練在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天是來告訴你們一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賺大錢的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十三話 生存競賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼放心隼人跟那種
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來路不明的人一起賽車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那是什麼比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一定不是被公認的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只求阿斯拉達沒事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對隼人要有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經驗是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定隼人可以從不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽中學到不同的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要賭一賭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一組
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的比賽?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是比賽的基本條件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才把你借出來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的隊員好像不太贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來參加這次比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在的我有一種
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想來參加比賽的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就帶你去看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天比賽的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來…慢一點 慢一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那種小孩子用的常識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種比賽裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是不太管用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起跑點是一座
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被封鎖的鬼城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先呢要穿過這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路面非常狹窄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過的時候請小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將接近一個90度的轉彎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來是連續的彎曲道路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你所看到的路面非常狹窄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也很急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果技術不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是開快車超車的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易就撞到牆壁的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著是要穿過這個廢工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是一個被廢棄的工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有看到一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央有一個路口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要從那裏穿過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意 跑道寬度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只容許一部車子前行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路面不良 障礙很多 請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道要注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條通道在以前是專門用於
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行駛機器人和搬運機器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會凹凸不平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要小心駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓車子撞壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你害怕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在退出還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑 這種難度嚇不倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 就是要有這種氣魄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來就是要經過前面的吊橋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險 快加速
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座吊橋換了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只被吊高了一點點而沒被拆掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此車手們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要快速的飛躍而過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車會掉河裏面去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼不早點告訴我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意速度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已開得太快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?這裏的彎度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是很大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達說得沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的彎道似乎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼特別之處
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你這麼想就錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一條看起來平坦緩和的彎道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是慢慢下坡而且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彎度慢慢變大的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被騙而拚命加速的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到發現不對勁的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人已經躺在山坡底下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 中餐讓你破費了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我們跑過的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是明天比賽的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成績是以兩輛車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達終點的點數的合計
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於兩輛車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都必須到達終點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是比賽絕對的條件之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以實際上是一場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相干擾對方的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼別的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他隊員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下去找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他們在家才好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛瑞在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛瑞 有人找你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是加賀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天來是告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個賺大錢的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要藉助一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的力量幫助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賺大錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 葛瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的比賽搭檔 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫風見隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑啊
